::KitKat::

She as she walked towards her quarters, she hears Time Bomb ask 
Phobia to be thier leader.  Now she felt hurt. She thought they would 
have chosen her to lead them. She hung her head and walked to her 
quarters. She closed the door behind her.  She walked over tot he 
sink and looked at her reflection in the mirror.
"Yeah, Their right, I couldn't lead a hungry Sharkticon to a floating 
carcas." She looked down and sighed, still leaning against she sink.
